export default {
  a11y: true,
  allowHTML: true,
  animateFill: true,
  animation: 'shift-away',
  appendTo: () => document.body,
  aria: 'describedby',
  arrow: false,
  arrowTransform: '',
  arrowType: 'sharp',
  autoFocus: true,
  boundary: 'scrollParent',
  content: '',
  delay: [0, 20],
  distance: 10,
  duration: [325, 275],
  flip: true,
  flipBehavior: 'flip',
  followCursor: false,
